[{"id":"VR023969","type":"mcq","stimulusHtml":"<p class=\"stem_paragraph\">Three charged particles are near each other but isolated from other objects. Particle <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"L\"><math alttext=\"L\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mstyle><mrow><mi>L</mi></mrow></mstyle></math></span></span> has a charge of <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"positive 2.0 microcoulombs\"><math alttext=\"positive 2.0 microcoulombs\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mstyle><mrow><mo>+</mo><mn>2.0</mn><mtext> </mtext><mtext>μ</mtext><mtext>C</mtext></mrow></mstyle></math></span></span> and is located <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"4.0 centimeters\"><math alttext=\"4.0 centimeters\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mstyle><mrow><mtext>4.0 cm</mtext></mrow></mstyle></math></span></span> above the origin on the positive <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"y\"><math alttext=\"y\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mstyle><mrow><mi>y</mi></mrow></mstyle></math></span></span>-axis. Particle <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"M\"><math alttext=\"M\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mstyle><mrow><mi>M</mi></mrow></mstyle></math></span></span> has a charge of <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"negative 4.0 microcoulombs\"><math alttext=\"negative 4.0 microcoulombs\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mstyle><mrow><mo>−</mo><mn>4.0</mn><mtext> </mtext><mtext>μ</mtext><mtext>C</mtext></mrow></mstyle></math></span></span> and is located <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"8.0 centimeters\"><math alttext=\"8.0 centimeters\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mstyle><mrow><mtext>8.0 cm</mtext></mrow></mstyle></math></span></span> directly below particle <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"L\"><math alttext=\"L\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mstyle><mrow><mi>L</mi></mrow></mstyle></math></span></span>. Particles <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"L\"><math alttext=\"L\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mstyle><mrow><mi>L</mi></mrow></mstyle></mat